Email: plkfsdevelopers@gmail.com

Support Hours: Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 6 PM (Your Timezone)

Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

1. How do I reset my password?

If you've forgotten your password, follow these steps:

Open the app and go to the Login screen.

Click Forgot Password? and enter your registered email.

Follow the instructions in the email to reset your password.

2. How do I delete my account?

To delete your account:

Navigate to Settings within the app.

Scroll down to Account Settings.

Select Delete Account and confirm your request.

Your data will be permanently deleted within 7 days.

3. Why am I not receiving notifications?

Ensure notifications are enabled in both:

Your device settings (Settings > Notifications > No Contact AI)

App settings (Settings > Notification Preferences)

If the issue persists, try restarting your phone or reinstalling the app.

4. How do I report a bug or provide feedback?

We appreciate your feedback! You can report issues or send suggestions by emailing [Insert Support Email] or using the in-app Feedback section under Settings.

Troubleshooting

App Crashes or Freezes

Ensure your app is updated to the latest version.

Restart your phone and relaunch the app.

If issues persist, reinstall the app.

Subscription Issues

If you're experiencing billing issues:

Check your subscription status in App Store/Google Play.

